{
  "stem": "20405.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he became very close friend with the-- with the head of the-- of this ghetto, an officer, a-- another German officer, call him Vichencelli, which-- that Jewish guy was a spy for us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- he was telling to-- to the Germans where we're living there-- Jewish people, the rich people, and-- and from the time, they start to get all the gold, all the money from the rich people and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made the first transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because like I said, was about 20, 50 meters from the-- from the ghetto was the train station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- they took away the old neighborhood the-- the first time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put in the trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When they return, were saying eight horses or 50-- 40 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Those trains was only for horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were putting all the sick people in there at the beginning, and then all the families, whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Filled up the trains, closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the back was a kind of a-- of the wagons-- was a kind of a-- a window, a little window.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were putting some wires, those pointed wires, just to don't let-- not to let anybody get away from there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was watching all those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they were taking some other Jewish people from some other neighborhoods, especially the poor neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we had-- not all the Jews was rich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they say now all the Jewish people are rich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's just ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were too many poor people over there, and working hard too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were taking the other people from the other neighborhoods and bringing them right-- right in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
